<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">I looted Talin Odonals corpse on the ramp before you zone into Halas.<p>

In case you are wondering, this is the Male NPC that stands near the fire near the merchants looking like a big dufus. If you hail him, he says something akin to <br>
"Brrr...It's cold out here!"  Anyway, the item that I looted off of him is described as<br>
"One Quarter of Elixer" and I'm interested in what this is for. I'm a shaman of the 8th level (No I didnt kill him, someone just left the corpse laying there) and if this can be used for some good experience, I'd appreciate some information if anyone is privy to it.<p>

Please, for all you sarcastic people, don't reply if you don't have some real information.<br>
This Forum is for us to learn from, not for abuse of one another.<p>

Thank you.<p>

Kaetlyn of the Bertoxxulous Server</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
