<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">Just a note on the Elixir to Young Warriors Quest.  Just for fun I mixed up the delivery order and found it does not matter what order you deliver the Elixir in.  So, quickest route is Talin O'Donal, Brydin McGill, Megan O'Rielly, Arnis McLish.  Works well at lvl 5 and 6 if you camp the Gnolls at BB entrance. <p>

Get Elixir and deliver to all four in order above.  Camp Gnolls until your Inventory is Full Up with LOOT.  Go to Halas and sell loot and turn in empty bottle.  Get new bottle and repeat.  Quick way to lvl from 5 to 7 if you're a warrior.</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
